  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to lxqt-openssh-askpass</title>

    <para>
      The <application>lxqt-openssh-askpass</application> package is a GUI
      to query credentials on behalf of other programs.
    </para>

    &lfs130_checked;

